The paper deals with the t-Partial-Vertex-Cover problem, which is a combinatorial optimization problem. The paper focuses on the integrality gap lower bounds on strong LP and SDP relaxations derived by various lift-and-project systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Other likely sub-categories include cs.CC (Computational Complexity), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), cs.GT (Discrete Mathematics), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
